28
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:20,220
Nothing, I was afraid 4th Prince would laugh at me.

29
00:02:20,220 --> 00:02:21,200
Why?

30
00:02:22,420 --> 00:02:23,825
This magnolia hairpin,

31
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:26,040
although I've kept it until now,

32
00:02:26,820 --> 00:02:29,685
I unknowingly put it on today.

33
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:32,318
And then...

34
00:02:32,740 --> 00:02:34,183
And then what?

35
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:37,287
And then...

36
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:41,931
Are you willing to marry me?

37
00:02:47,915 --> 00:02:50,337
Right now, I'm not willing to marry you.

38
00:02:50,540 --> 00:02:51,640
You're not willing to?

39
00:02:55,570 --> 00:02:57,263
If I have to marry the Crown Prince,

40
00:02:57,263 --> 00:02:59,074
I would rather die.

41
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,507
That won't do either.

42
00:03:00,920 --> 00:03:01,947
Don't forget,

43
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:04,176
I saved your life.

44
00:03:04,176 --> 00:03:05,676
Without my permission,

45
00:03:05,676 --> 00:03:07,340
you're not allowed to die.

46
00:03:12,235 --> 00:03:13,951
Why the Crown Prince suddenly wants you,

47
00:03:13,951 --> 00:03:15,577
I'm sure you're aware of it.

48
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:18,084
If I ask for your hand from Father now,

49
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:21,405
then won't I be snatching you from the Crown Prince?

50
00:03:22,080 --> 00:03:23,170
Going down that train of thought,

51
00:03:23,170 --> 00:03:24,981
what concerns Father the most?

52
00:03:25,920 --> 00:03:27,320
I'm afraid that if I put in the request,

53
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:29,532
it would rouse Father's suspicions.

54
00:03:32,060 --> 00:03:33,711
So for now,

55
00:03:33,711 --> 00:03:35,174
no one dares to marry you.

56
00:03:39,100 --> 00:03:41,095
You can only wait.

57
00:03:42,740 --> 00:03:44,253
Wait?

58
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:49,510
Since you're already wearing my hairpin

59
00:03:49,510 --> 00:03:51,103
and said you want to marry me,

60
00:03:51,480 --> 00:03:53,332
what do you think you have to wait for?

61
00:03:57,100 --> 00:03:58,023
Thank you,

62
00:03:58,023 --> 00:03:59,718
