63
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,545
I didn't do anything.

64
00:04:01,545 --> 00:04:04,153
You merely fell sick at the right time.

65
00:04:04,153 --> 00:04:05,353
Hurry and go back,

66
00:04:05,353 --> 00:04:06,475
you've only just recovered.

67
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:08,379
You should rest more and recuperate.

68
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:10,429
