81
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:16,158
What kind of plans can I have?

82
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:17,737
As a servant,

83
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:20,616
I cannot make my own decisions.

84
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:24,703
Furthermore, this is your decision to make.

85
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:26,746
Why are you concerned about me?

86
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:30,276
You have someone else in your heart, don't you?

87
00:05:31,644 --> 00:05:34,491
Why do you always ask me this question?

88
00:05:35,220 --> 00:05:37,149
I have no control over what becomes of me.

89
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:38,960
Don't tell me that you

90
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:42,814
want to control my heart as well?

91
00:05:43,280 --> 00:05:45,554
I hope it's not 4th Brother.

92
00:05:45,554 --> 00:05:48,016
Otherwise, you'll only suffer

93
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:50,152
and waste

94
00:05:50,152 --> 00:05:52,102
the efforts I've put in to help you today.

95
00:05:54,206 --> 00:05:58,293
Whether or not that is the case, it has nothing to do with you.

96
00:05:58,293 --> 00:06:00,369
In any case, both of us know

97
00:06:00,369 --> 00:06:01,553
this matter

98
00:06:01,553 --> 00:06:04,130
can only be decided by the Emperor

99
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:08,658
If you're willing only to abide by Father's decision,

100
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:11,073
then just take it that

101
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:14,928
I did not say the things I just said.

102
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:45,857
- Master.
- Master.

103
