Mother.

104
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:15,230
8th Prince.

105
00:07:23,728 --> 00:07:25,516
Mother.

106
00:07:26,508 --> 00:07:28,279
I just talked with the Physician.

107
00:07:28,279 --> 00:07:30,485
He said that you're getting better

108
00:07:30,485 --> 00:07:32,436
and you can get up from the bed soon.

109
00:07:35,520 --> 00:07:37,591
Even if I can leave this bed,

110
00:07:38,640 --> 00:07:40,152
there won't be many days left

111
00:07:40,152 --> 00:07:41,845
for me to walk around.

112
00:07:41,845 --> 00:07:43,999
You still have many days.

113
00:07:46,972 --> 00:07:49,526
If I can live for one more day,

114
00:07:50,455 --> 00:07:51,346
you'll have to suffer one more day

115
00:07:51,346 --> 00:07:53,287
on my behalf.

116
00:07:54,681 --> 00:07:57,699
Mother, don't say that.

117
00:07:57,699 --> 00:08:01,182
If it weren't for the fact that I was born with a lowly status,

118
00:08:02,204 --> 00:08:05,408
when everybody nominated you as Crown Prince,

119
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:09,077
your father

120
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:14,450
would definitely have let you be Crown Prince

121
00:08:14,450 --> 00:08:17,111
Whenever I think about this,

122
00:08:19,060 --> 00:08:22,305
I feel like I've let you down.

123
00:08:22,305 --> 00:08:24,992
Two completely unrelated matters,

124
00:08:24,992 --> 00:08:26,903
why have you linked them together?

125
00:08:26,903 --> 00:08:29,696
This is the fickleness of the world.

126
00:08:31,520 --> 00:08:34,387
Who doesn't look at birth status?

127
00:08:41,166 --> 00:08:43,930
If I came from a good family,

128
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:47,575
your path

129
00:08:50,199 --> 00:08:53,427
wouldn't have to be so rocky

130
00:08:54,333 --> 00:08:58,589
Mother, tell me frankly,

131
00:08:58,589 --> 00:09:00,400
in your eyes,

132
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:03,458
how are my achievements to date?

133
00:09:03,458 --> 00:09:05,130
You definitely have not...

134
00:09:06,570 --> 00:09:10,703
You definitely have not lost to the other Princes.

135
00:09:12,421 --> 00:09:17,529
Your Father once told me,

136
00:09:17,529 --> 00:09:19,866
in terms of ability and talent,

137
00:09:21,477 --> 00:09:24,588
many of the Princes cannot compare.

138
00:09:26,376 --> 00:09:28,350
It's just that

139
00:09:30,556 --> 00:09:32,715
it's only because of me

140
00:09:35,478 --> 00:09:38,683
that you can't be Crown Prince.

141
00:09:39,186 --> 00:09:41,167
What is bestowed by others

142
00:09:41,167 --> 00:09:43,889
cannot be compared to what one earns by his own means.

143
00:09:43,889 --> 00:09:45,786
If I didn't have the strength,

144
00:09:45,786 --> 00:09:48,087
would I dare to rise to the challenge.

145
00:09:49,760 --> 00:09:52,034
You have drive.

146
00:09:52,034 --> 00:09:53,985
Mother, you should feel comforted.

147
00:09:53,985 --> 00:09:56,191
With a son like you

148
00:09:57,800 --> 00:10:00,742
I have no regrets in life.

149
00:10:02,855 --> 00:10:04,828
These many years,

150
00:10:05,520 --> 00:10:07,522
everything I've done

151
00:10:08,451 --> 00:10:10,062
was all to

152
00:10:10,062 --> 00:10:13,141
enable us to gain a sense of self respect

153
00:10:13,141 --> 00:10:15,417
and not let others belittle us.

154
00:10:16,800 --> 00:10:20,386
Seeing you with such sureness like this,

155
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:25,726
I believe you will succeed.

156
00:10:27,920 --> 00:10:30,277
Mother will help you.

157
00:10:32,716 --> 00:10:37,979
I will... I will definitely help you.

158
00:10:37,979 --> 00:10:40,526
Nursing your body back to health

159
00:10:40,526 --> 00:10:44,697
to become the Empress Dowager will be your help to me.

160
00:10:46,044 --> 00:10:47,782
No matter

161
00:10:47,782 --> 00:10:49,954
how lowly our births,

162
00:10:49,954 --> 00:10:53,914
we will surely atttain wealth and rank in our future.

163
00:10:53,914 --> 00:10:56,446
Alright.

164
00:10:58,350 --> 00:11:00,301
In the future...

165
00:11:06,524 --> 00:11:09,032
All right.

166
00:11:10,193 --> 00:11:14,047
I know you have many things to do,

167
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:18,598
go back first.

168
00:11:18,598 --> 00:11:20,874
I want to spend more time with Mother.

169
00:11:22,731 --> 00:11:24,496
I'm tired.

170
00:11:26,493 --> 00:11:29,419
I want to rest.

171
00:11:41,261 --> 00:11:43,722
Don't worry about anything,

172
00:11:43,722 --> 00:11:47,298
I will resolve everything.

173
00:11:59,698 --> 00:12:01,648
Master.

174
00:12:01,648 --> 00:12:04,992
The only way I can help

175
00:12:06,663 --> 00:12:10,611
is to not drag you down.

176
00:12:13,095 --> 00:12:16,760
Mistress, it's time for your medicine.

177
00:12:16,760 --> 00:12:18,527
From now on,

178
00:12:18,527 --> 00:12:22,987
I cannot eat medicine anymore.

179
00:12:23,730 --> 00:12:26,145
Pour it away in secret.

180
00:12:27,445 --> 00:12:30,292
Don't let anyone know.

181
00:12:30,292 --> 00:12:32,275
Yes.

182
00:12:45,464 --> 00:12:48,297
Jie`jie, what's wrong with you?

183
00:12:50,154 --> 00:12:51,826
Are you all right?

184
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:55,595
The lotuses, Jie`jie has drawn,

185
00:12:55,595 --> 00:12:58,096
were really beautiful and lifelike.

186
00:12:58,096 --> 00:12:59,846
Ruined just like this.

187
00:12:59,846 --> 00:13:00,929
What a pity.

188
00:13:00,929 --> 00:13:03,065
Ruoxi Jie`jie, bad news!

189
00:13:04,040 --> 00:13:06,144
Bad news! Mistress Liang has passed away!

190
00:13:06,144 --> 00:13:09,425
What? She's passed away?

191
00:13:09,425 --> 00:13:10,765
Why is it so sudden?

192
00:13:10,765 --> 00:13:12,112
It's not really sudden.

193
00:13:12,112 --> 00:13:14,796
I heard that about a week ago she was already unwell.

194
00:13:14,796 --> 00:13:15,936
She even saw the physician,

195
00:13:15,936 --> 00:13:17,422
but no one took it to heart.

196
00:13:17,422 --> 00:13:20,805
But who knew she would leave so suddenly.

197
00:13:23,057 --> 00:13:25,275
The 8th Prince must be devastated.

198
00:13:25,275 --> 00:13:27,128
But of course.

199
00:13:59,280 --> 00:14:02,306
" Myriad things are all different and who believes in Taoism.
(Classic poem about a pear flower)

200
00:14:02,306 --> 00:14:05,378
Not in line with all the other flowers.

201
00:14:05,378 --> 00:14:09,390
Her spirit is distinct and her character is noble.

202
00:14:09,390 --> 00:14:12,655
Could not be distinguishable on earth.

203
00:14:14,095 --> 00:14:16,277
When she returns back to Yao Tai,
(eastern heaven)

204
00:14:16,277 --> 00:14:21,014
only in the Goddess realm can her beauty and elegance  be viewed."

205
00:14:23,011 --> 00:14:24,783
Mistress Liang,

206
00:14:24,783 --> 00:14:28,730
Ruoxi will send you off from here.

207
00:14:56,753 --> 00:15:00,004
Stop!

208
00:15:11,021 --> 00:15:15,897
Move on!

209
00:15:18,414 --> 00:15:21,084
So this is the Emperor's love.

210
00:15:21,084 --> 00:15:24,985
But a mere moment's worth.

211
00:15:30,111 --> 00:15:31,237
Miss Ruoxi.

212
00:15:31,237 --> 00:15:33,662
The Emperor would like to see you.

213
00:15:33,662 --> 00:15:34,830
I'll go immediately.

214
00:15:34,830 --> 00:15:36,409
Yes.

215
00:15:39,683 --> 00:15:40,721
Your Majesty.

216
00:15:40,721 --> 00:15:42,354
Ruoxi.

217
00:15:43,190 --> 00:15:45,628
The Crown Prince said that the person kneeling by the back wall was you.

218
00:15:47,269 --> 00:15:49,204
Was it really you?

219
00:15:50,995 --> 00:15:53,397
In the past, I've been to Mistress Liang's palace

220
00:15:53,397 --> 00:15:55,359
to help her draw some designs.

221
00:15:55,359 --> 00:15:58,831
She was very pleased and complimented them.

222
00:15:58,831 --> 00:16:00,535
Today, I just happened to pass by

223
00:16:00,535 --> 00:16:03,175
and couldn't help but kowtow to her,

224
00:16:03,175 --> 00:16:04,473
so that I wouldn't disappoint

225
00:16:04,473 --> 00:16:07,185
her goodwill toward me in the past.

226
00:16:07,185 --> 00:16:08,453
You may rise.

227
00:16:14,156 --> 00:16:15,733
If you have the time,

228
00:16:15,733 --> 00:16:17,253
go and see the 8th Prince.

229
00:16:17,253 --> 00:16:18,732
Advise him,

230
00:16:18,732 --> 00:16:21,001
that even if he is grieving, he has to mind his health.

231
00:16:21,001 --> 00:16:22,733
Yes.

232
00:16:23,407 --> 00:16:24,637
You are dismissed.

233
00:16:50,626 --> 00:16:53,040
Greetings, 14th Prince.

234
00:16:56,943 --> 00:16:58,963
One can call you heartless,

235
00:16:58,963 --> 00:17:01,510
but you actually kowtowed before Concubine Liang's palace.

236
00:17:02,562 --> 00:17:04,609
One can call you compassionate,

237
00:17:04,609 --> 00:17:07,353
but since 8th Brother's mother passed away,

238
00:17:07,353 --> 00:17:08,962
he has been grieving

239
00:17:08,962 --> 00:17:10,772
and holing himself up at home.

240
00:17:10,772 --> 00:17:12,602
His health has never been good

241
00:17:12,602 --> 00:17:14,666
and now his leg ailment has suddenly flared up

242
00:17:14,666 --> 00:17:16,139
to where even walking is a problem.

243
00:17:16,905 --> 00:17:18,679
Even completely unrelated people

244
00:17:18,679 --> 00:17:20,086
know how to say a few consoling lines.

245
00:17:20,690 --> 00:17:21,950
But you remain indifferent,

246
00:17:21,950 --> 00:17:23,351
as though you don't know.

247
00:17:23,351 --> 00:17:26,705
You didn't even off the basic words of asking how he is.

248
00:17:26,705 --> 00:17:30,050
Ruoxi, do you really not care about

249
00:17:30,050 --> 00:17:32,436
how 8th Brother looked after you in the past?

250
00:17:32,436 --> 00:17:33,415
Let's not talk of the past,

251
00:17:33,415 --> 00:17:34,901
but even recently

252
00:17:34,901 --> 00:17:36,108
if it weren't for 8th Brother

253
00:17:36,108 --> 00:17:39,237
you'd probably be the Crown Prince's woman by now.

254
00:17:39,237 --> 00:17:40,563
Ruoxi,

255
00:17:40,938 --> 00:17:45,575
do you know how disappointed 8th Brother is?

256
00:17:45,575 --> 00:17:47,661
14th Prince.

257
00:17:48,280 --> 00:17:51,308
Do you know what longing feels like?

258
00:17:51,875 --> 00:17:54,906
It's like a needle in your heart.

259
00:17:54,906 --> 00:17:57,038
How the heart is wounded, how the heart hurts,

260
00:17:57,038 --> 00:17:59,142
you don't understand.

261
00:18:00,118 --> 00:18:03,504
Since two people can no longer be together,

262
00:18:03,504 --> 00:18:07,734
then why hinder them by doing things that make it so much harder to let go.

263
00:18:07,734 --> 00:18:11,170
To let their hearts continue to hurt.

264
00:18:12,633 --> 00:18:15,350
Now, the more it hurts

265
00:18:15,350 --> 00:18:18,361
the easier it will be for him to forget.

266
00:18:18,361 --> 00:18:19,244
I would rather

267
00:18:19,244 --> 00:18:21,434
he feel the hurt now, then

268
00:18:21,434 --> 00:18:23,059
he will forget me completely.

269
00:18:23,865 --> 00:18:27,442
From now on, he won't think of me anymore.

270
00:18:27,442 --> 00:18:29,375
A needle in the heart?

271
00:18:31,834 --> 00:18:33,292
What feels like heartlessness

272
00:18:33,292 --> 00:18:34,939
is actually heartfelt concern.

273
00:18:35,203 --> 00:18:36,989
If you're willing to wait,

274
00:18:36,989 --> 00:18:39,104
it's still possible.

275
00:18:39,104 --> 00:18:40,690
Wait?

276
00:18:41,660 --> 00:18:44,498
There's no turning back anymore.

277
00:18:45,520 --> 00:18:46,534
Moreover,

278
00:18:47,400 --> 00:18:50,428
will His Majesty let me wait forever?

279
00:18:50,428 --> 00:18:55,329
Then can you forget 8th Brother?

280
00:18:55,329 --> 00:18:57,223
I've already forgotten.

281
00:18:57,223 --> 00:18:59,763
I can see that your situation fits the old saying:

282
00:18:59,763 --> 00:19:02,345
'Help each other when both are in humble circumstances'.

283
00:19:02,345 --> 00:19:04,567
I'm the silly one here.

284
00:19:04,567 --> 00:19:06,418
Alright then,

285
00:19:06,418 --> 00:19:08,618
since you've already made it so clear,

286
00:19:08,618 --> 00:19:09,861
from now on,

287
00:19:09,861 --> 00:19:12,466
I can at least put down this burden.

288
00:19:12,466 --> 00:19:15,141
What happens after today,

289
00:19:15,141 --> 00:19:16,324
even I cannot predict.

290
00:19:16,324 --> 00:19:17,942
From now on,

291
00:19:17,942 --> 00:19:19,964
you have to be very careful.

292
00:19:19,964 --> 00:19:22,293
What you can avoid, avoid.

293
00:19:22,293 --> 00:19:23,547
For many things,

294
00:19:23,547 --> 00:19:24,933
it only takes a moment

295
00:19:24,933 --> 00:19:26,008
to make a huge difference.

296
00:19:26,008 --> 00:19:27,952
It won't always be like today

297
00:19:27,952 --> 00:19:30,423
when people can save you.

298
00:19:30,423 --> 00:19:32,253
When a dog is forced into a corner

299
00:19:32,253 --> 00:19:34,228
it will react in panic and without reason.

300
00:19:34,228 --> 00:19:35,714
If we're affected,

301
00:19:35,714 --> 00:19:36,782
the few of us

302
00:19:36,782 --> 00:19:39,737
may not be able to ensure your safety.

303
00:19:39,737 --> 00:19:42,151
I understand.

304
00:19:42,151 --> 00:19:43,795
That's good.

305
00:20:28,029 --> 00:20:31,535
It's snowing. Why are you daydreaming?

306
00:20:32,741 --> 00:20:35,102
I'm not daydreaming.

307
00:20:35,102 --> 00:20:36,434
I'm admiring the blossoms.

308
00:20:39,360 --> 00:20:41,914
You've watched them grow onto the walls.

309
00:20:43,840 --> 00:20:46,140
What are you thinking about?

310
00:20:48,220 --> 00:20:51,249
The days in this palace are getting harder to get by.

311
00:20:52,080 --> 00:20:53,506
I have to be scared of this

312
00:20:53,506 --> 00:20:55,428
and of that.

313
00:20:56,280 --> 00:20:58,011
So I was thinking

314
00:20:58,011 --> 00:20:59,885
if I could find a small place

315
00:20:59,885 --> 00:21:01,835
and ensconce myself in it,

316
00:21:02,400 --> 00:21:04,461
it would be safer than staying in this palace.

317
00:21:10,716 --> 00:21:12,727
Have I said something wrong?

318
00:21:12,727 --> 00:21:14,956
Not everyone likes to hear the truth.

319
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:18,114
Women are natural actresses.

320
00:21:18,840 --> 00:21:20,204
Lies, I know how to tell them.

321
00:21:21,440 --> 00:21:22,651
If 4th Prince

322
00:21:22,651 --> 00:21:25,173
wants me to pretend to be gentle and sentimental,

323
00:21:25,640 --> 00:21:27,541
I am willing to act out this farce.

324
00:21:28,840 --> 00:21:29,910
But I feel that

325
00:21:30,520 --> 00:21:32,557
you prefer to hear the truth

326
00:21:33,160 --> 00:21:34,833
even if it hurts.

327
00:21:35,960 --> 00:21:37,062
Where's the hairpin?

328
00:21:38,440 --> 00:21:40,027
It's in the house.

329
00:21:40,027 --> 00:21:41,897
And the earrings I sent you last year

330
00:21:41,897 --> 00:21:44,212
are also left unused in the house.

331
00:21:44,540 --> 00:21:47,509
What a waste of my sentiments.

332
00:21:48,420 --> 00:21:50,999
I'm wearing the necklace.

333
00:21:54,035 --> 00:21:56,154
Ruoxi.

334
00:21:56,600 --> 00:21:59,722
Do you not understand your own heart?

335
00:22:00,640 --> 00:22:03,013
Too many fears and too many concerns.

336
00:22:03,013 --> 00:22:07,099
Every day you try to balance yourself and you have become too careful.

337
00:22:10,341 --> 00:22:12,590
It hurts. Why did you hit me?

338
00:22:12,590 --> 00:22:14,285
Hurry and go back,

339
00:22:14,285 --> 00:22:16,636
you can daydream in front of the heater.

340
00:22:18,280 --> 00:22:19,979
Aren't you leaving?

341
00:22:37,640 --> 00:22:39,779
I don't understand my own heart.

342
00:22:40,740 --> 00:22:42,721
What is it saying?

343
00:22:42,721 --> 00:22:46,141
Can he understand what my heart is saying?

344
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:48,642
Actually,

345
00:22:48,642 --> 00:22:52,000
I need to understand my thoughts and feelings.

346
00:22:52,160 --> 00:22:53,673
More importantly,

347
00:22:53,673 --> 00:22:56,142
I need to know how to live safely

348
00:22:56,142 --> 00:22:58,285
in this tumultuous palace.

349
00:23:03,027 --> 00:23:04,299
It's been more than two months

350
00:23:04,299 --> 00:23:05,823
since I last saw the 8th Prince.

351
00:23:06,420 --> 00:23:07,443
His grief...

352
00:23:07,443 --> 00:23:09,686
Has it lessened?

353
00:23:14,771 --> 00:23:16,843
A person's heart is hard to understand.

354
00:23:16,843 --> 00:23:18,763
I can't read it clearly.

355
00:23:19,320 --> 00:23:21,644
But I must make a decision.

356
00:23:22,400 --> 00:23:26,195
I know that much.

357
00:23:47,600 --> 00:23:50,205
Cutting ties is not easy.

358
00:23:51,280 --> 00:23:53,107
It will hurt.

359
00:24:24,200 --> 00:24:26,173
Greetings, 10th Prince. Greetings, 14th Prince.

360
00:24:26,840 --> 00:24:28,666
Ruoxi, what's wrong?

361
00:24:28,666 --> 00:24:29,865
For this year's New Year eve,

362
00:24:29,865 --> 00:24:31,504
do you want us to bring you outside the palace for fun?

363
00:24:31,504 --> 00:24:32,533
10th Prince.

364
00:24:32,533 --> 00:24:34,430
Can you leave the palace on your own first?

365
00:24:34,880 --> 00:24:36,420
I need to speak with 14th Prince.

366
00:24:38,000 --> 00:24:40,303
What is it now that you're keeping from me?

367
00:24:40,520 --> 00:24:41,921
What do I have to do with it?

368
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:44,029
I don't know what she wants to say.

369
00:24:44,029 --> 00:24:46,033
If you want to glare, glare at her.

370
00:24:46,360 --> 00:24:47,247
You...

371
00:24:48,080 --> 00:24:49,144
These past days

372
00:24:49,144 --> 00:24:51,041
I saw you and 10th Fujin from afar.

373
00:24:51,041 --> 00:24:52,156
Before I could greet 10th Fujin,

374
00:24:52,156 --> 00:24:54,142
you took her and ran away.

375
00:24:54,142 --> 00:24:55,917
Tell me, why are you avoiding me?

376
00:24:55,917 --> 00:24:56,985
If you want to settle a score,

377
00:24:56,985 --> 00:24:58,564
then we should settle things clearly.

378
00:25:00,160 --> 00:25:02,255
I'm not going talk nonsense with you.

379
00:25:02,255 --> 00:25:03,573
Besides, I can't out talk you.

380
00:25:03,573 --> 00:25:06,506
You two can talk about whatever you want to talk about.

381
00:25:11,360 --> 00:25:13,054
You saw 10th Fujin from afar.

382
00:25:13,054 --> 00:25:13,982
Not only did you not hide,

383
00:25:13,982 --> 00:25:15,515
were you still going up to greet her?

384
00:25:16,280 --> 00:25:17,140
I was bluffing.

385
00:25:17,840 --> 00:25:19,430
I actually wanted to avoid her,

386
00:25:19,430 --> 00:25:21,506
but I didn't think that 10th Prince saw me too.

387
00:25:21,506 --> 00:25:23,108
He blocked 10th Fujin's line of sight

388
00:25:23,108 --> 00:25:24,687
and ran away faster than I could!

389
00:25:27,591 --> 00:25:29,368
I don't know when 10th Fujin's heart

390
00:25:29,368 --> 00:25:31,378
can open up and understand.

391
00:25:31,378 --> 00:25:33,803
Even you and I know 10th Brother's feelings.

392
00:25:33,803 --> 00:25:35,949
They're the only ones who still don't know it.

393
00:25:37,200 --> 00:25:38,456
The ones involved are always clueless

394
00:25:38,456 --> 00:25:39,757
while the observers understand

395
00:25:40,740 --> 00:25:41,846
But when the time comes

396
00:25:41,846 --> 00:25:43,286
they will understand.

397
00:25:43,286 --> 00:25:45,469
What do you want from me?

398
00:25:53,640 --> 00:25:54,687
It seems like it's a bracelet.

399
00:25:55,440 --> 00:25:56,327
What does this mean?

400
00:25:56,327 --> 00:25:58,124
Help me return it to the 8th Prince.

401
00:25:58,960 --> 00:26:00,128
But there's no hurry,

402
00:26:00,920 --> 00:26:01,692
just hold on to it

403
00:26:01,692 --> 00:26:03,395
and return it to him when he's feeling better.

404
00:26:03,395 --> 00:26:05,917
Why are you asking me to do something that would only harm him?

405
00:26:05,917 --> 00:26:07,310
Return it yourself.

406
00:26:07,310 --> 00:26:09,235
This bangle is too valuable.

407
00:26:09,235 --> 00:26:10,361
I must return it.

408
00:26:11,880 --> 00:26:12,868
Just take it as I'm begging you.

409
00:26:17,960 --> 00:26:19,323
4th Brother and 13th Brother are coming.

410
00:26:19,974 --> 00:26:21,831
Stop fooling around.

411
00:26:24,200 --> 00:26:25,823
4th Brother, 13th Brother.

412
00:26:25,823 --> 00:26:27,265
14th Brother.

413
00:26:27,265 --> 00:26:30,919
- Greetings, 4th Prince, 13th Prince.
- Rise.

414
00:26:30,919 --> 00:26:33,014
4th Brother, are you leaving the palace?

415
00:26:33,014 --> 00:26:34,068
Not yet.

416
00:26:34,068 --> 00:26:36,226
I need to go now to visit mother.

417
00:26:36,226 --> 00:26:38,526
Fine, then I'll go first.

418
00:26:43,240 --> 00:26:47,582
It would be impolite of me to decline. Thank you.

419
00:27:08,671 --> 00:27:10,427
No explanation?

420
00:27:11,720 --> 00:27:14,460
4th Prince can believe it or not.

421
00:27:14,460 --> 00:27:16,118
I only have one sentence.

422
00:27:16,118 --> 00:27:18,200
It's definitely not what you're thinking.

423
00:27:18,200 --> 00:27:19,486
I haven't even considered anything

424
00:27:19,486 --> 00:27:20,994
and you've already confessed?

425
00:27:21,680 --> 00:27:23,348
It seems you and 14th Prince

426
00:27:23,348 --> 00:27:24,802
have something going on.

427
00:27:25,480 --> 00:27:28,120
I always thought that you were on good terms with 14th Brother and the others.

428
00:27:28,120 --> 00:27:29,717
Giving gifts

429
00:27:29,717 --> 00:27:31,032
is not unusual.

430
00:27:31,720 --> 00:27:34,151
But you're actually rejecting my assumptions.

431
00:27:34,151 --> 00:27:37,387
It's rare that you are so quick to clarify your actions.

432
00:27:40,400 --> 00:27:42,521
I don't care what 14th Brother thinks

433
00:27:42,521 --> 00:27:43,542
and I don't care to monitor it.

434
00:27:44,471 --> 00:27:46,793
If you want to exchange gifts and laugh together, that's fine,

435
00:27:47,838 --> 00:27:49,951
but I don't want to see

436
00:27:49,951 --> 00:27:51,855
the crying and fighting between you like last time.

437
00:27:53,140 --> 00:27:54,270
I understand.

438
00:27:57,640 --> 00:27:59,920
Is there anything else?

439
00:28:01,360 --> 00:28:02,880
No.

440
00:28:04,790 --> 00:28:11,960
