441
00:28:11,960 --> 00:28:14,400
He's more generous than I had thought.

442
00:28:14,400 --> 00:28:17,400
He didn't say any "don't do this" and "don't do that."

443
00:28:18,000 --> 00:28:18,800
But,

444
00:28:18,800 --> 00:28:21,000
that 14th Prince is truly detestable.

445
00:28:21,000 --> 00:28:24,480
What's he trying to do?  Really.

446
00:28:26,160 --> 00:28:27,640
Reporting to Your Majesty,

447
00:28:27,640 --> 00:28:32,280
the investigation is complete and has uncovered something.

448
00:28:34,620 --> 00:28:37,460
Speak, what was the result.

449
00:28:37,460 --> 00:28:39,820
Everything that Zhengguo Gong reported was true.

450
00:28:39,820 --> 00:28:41,700
There's evidence of a revolt.

451
00:28:41,700 --> 00:28:43,700
Especially Qi Shiwu and Tou He'qi.

452
00:28:43,700 --> 00:28:48,140
They tried to gather everyone to support the Crown Prince in taking over the throne.

453
00:28:51,540 --> 00:28:52,700
Imperial Father,

454
00:28:52,700 --> 00:28:56,300
I have always treated them as drinking pals. I had no idea of their intentions.

455
00:28:56,300 --> 00:28:59,020
As for their plan to form a political faction...

456
00:28:59,020 --> 00:29:00,700
and the details of their evil plot,

457
00:29:00,700 --> 00:29:02,180
I know nothing about that.

458
00:29:02,180 --> 00:29:04,140
I really didn't know.

459
00:29:04,140 --> 00:29:05,660
If they are only your drinking pals,

460
00:29:05,660 --> 00:29:08,500
that's normal.

461
00:29:08,500 --> 00:29:10,340
But I'm afraid that their...

462
00:29:10,340 --> 00:29:11,920
real intention isn't about drinking wine.

463
00:29:11,920 --> 00:29:15,620
Qi Shiwu, Tou He'qi, Geng'e, and the rest,

464
00:29:15,620 --> 00:29:19,060
are guilty of gathering their men...

465
00:29:19,060 --> 00:29:21,460
in support of the Crown Prince.

466
00:29:21,460 --> 00:29:24,820
They shall be thrown into jail and severely punished.

467
00:29:24,820 --> 00:29:27,600
Investigate everybody involved in this case and...

468
00:29:27,600 --> 00:29:28,980
do not let anyone escape punishment.

469
00:29:28,980 --> 00:29:30,640
Yes.

470
00:29:54,660 --> 00:29:56,820
- I'm innocent!
- Go. Behave yourself!

471
00:29:56,820 --> 00:29:59,540
- Quickly.
- Let go!

472
00:29:59,540 --> 00:30:01,500
Walk quickly!

473
00:30:01,500 --> 00:30:02,380
Don't move!

474
00:30:02,380 --> 00:30:04,460
No!

475
00:30:04,460 --> 00:30:05,660
Hold him down.

476
00:30:05,660 --> 00:30:07,020
Don't move.

477
00:30:07,020 --> 00:30:09,660
Behave yourself. Don't move.

478
00:30:09,660 --> 00:30:11,100
Don't move.

479
00:30:13,060 --> 00:30:14,060
Hold him.

480
00:30:14,060 --> 00:30:15,380
No, don't.

481
00:30:15,380 --> 00:30:17,940
Behave yourself.

482
00:30:23,340 --> 00:30:25,140
Greetings, Mistress.

483
00:30:25,140 --> 00:30:26,260
Rise.

484
00:30:26,260 --> 00:30:28,460
4th Prince has sent me with a letter for you.

485
00:30:32,060 --> 00:30:32,900
Thank you for your trouble.

486
00:30:32,900 --> 00:30:34,220
I will leave now.

487
00:30:47,540 --> 00:30:50,040
[ Follow the path to the end of the water, ]

488
00:30:50,040 --> 00:30:53,820
[ sit down and look at the clouds generate.]

489
00:31:30,460 --> 00:31:34,420
Jie Jie, so many sheets of paper... are you practicing your writing?

490
00:31:34,940 --> 00:31:36,720
Practicing your writing can help calm your emotions.

491
00:31:36,720 --> 00:31:38,340
Try it.

492
00:31:39,380 --> 00:31:41,540
Jie Jie, I can't read.

493
00:31:42,620 --> 00:31:44,100
I'll teach you.

494
00:31:44,100 --> 00:31:45,980
Jie Jie, I still have a lot of work to do.

495
00:31:45,980 --> 00:31:47,940
I'll go now.

496
00:31:55,580 --> 00:31:56,600
Is everything prepared?

497
00:31:56,600 --> 00:31:58,260
It's almost done.

498
00:31:58,260 --> 00:31:59,580
Ruoxi Jie Jie.

499
00:32:00,340 --> 00:32:02,580
With the pillow that contains chrysanthemums made by you,

500
00:32:02,580 --> 00:32:05,020
I sleep much better.

501
00:32:05,020 --> 00:32:06,580
That's good.

502
00:32:06,580 --> 00:32:07,740
Is there anything else?

503
00:32:07,740 --> 00:32:10,220
I came to give a message.

504
00:32:10,220 --> 00:32:11,540
8th Bei'le Ye has returned.

505
00:32:11,540 --> 00:32:13,520
Jie Jie needs to prepare one more cup of tea.

506
00:32:13,520 --> 00:32:14,860
Alright.

507
00:33:02,900 --> 00:33:04,203
You piece of trash!

508
00:33:04,203 --> 00:33:05,689
Where were you looking?

509
00:33:07,393 --> 00:33:08,986
Your servant deserves to die.

510
00:33:09,580 --> 00:33:10,940
Rouxi?

511
00:33:10,940 --> 00:33:12,900
Are you alright?

512
00:33:12,900 --> 00:33:14,573
I'm fine.

513
00:33:14,573 --> 00:33:16,231
I'm not hurt anywhere that matters.

514
00:33:16,231 --> 00:33:18,335
I hope 10th Prince doesn't take offense.

515
00:33:18,335 --> 00:33:19,914
You come in and don't even greet anyone.

516
00:33:19,914 --> 00:33:21,075
You're bumping into everything,

517
00:33:21,075 --> 00:33:23,060
what's so urgent?

518
00:33:33,088 --> 00:33:34,460
Where's Imperial Father?

519
00:33:35,620 --> 00:33:37,020
The Emperor is still taking a nap and has not woken up yet.

520
00:33:37,020 --> 00:33:38,000
If 10th Prince could please wait a little while--

521
00:33:38,000 --> 00:33:38,940
Where's the tea?

522
00:33:38,940 --> 00:33:40,360
Don't you see the Princes are waiting?

523
00:33:40,360 --> 00:33:43,060
Miss Ruoxi is currently preparing the tea, she'll return immediately.

524
00:33:43,060 --> 00:33:45,040
Get out, all of you get out!

525
00:33:45,040 --> 00:33:46,740
Yes.

526
00:33:48,060 --> 00:33:49,460
10th Brother,

527
00:33:49,460 --> 00:33:51,380
just what kind of fight gave you this injury?

528
00:33:51,380 --> 00:33:53,440
Why are you using your hand to hide your face?

529
00:33:53,440 --> 00:33:54,360
Unless,

530
00:33:54,360 --> 00:33:57,020
fighting with women gives you a black eye?

531
00:33:58,060 --> 00:33:59,940
Even if I'm beaten by Imperial Father

532
00:33:59,940 --> 00:34:02,140
I have to divorce that shrew!

533
00:34:02,860 --> 00:34:04,120
Stop blocking your face with your hand.

534
00:34:04,120 --> 00:34:05,180
Let me go!

535
00:34:05,180 --> 00:34:07,420
Let me see just how bad it is.

536
00:34:08,180 --> 00:34:09,780
How can you bring a personal matter

537
00:34:09,780 --> 00:34:11,240
like this into the Imperial Palace?

538
00:34:11,240 --> 00:34:12,785
Quickly, go back.

539
00:34:13,980 --> 00:34:15,339
What was this about?

540
00:34:15,339 --> 00:34:16,980
Tell us.

541
00:34:16,980 --> 00:34:19,500
We can help you reason it out.

542
00:34:21,850 --> 00:34:24,544
8th Brother, you judge it as a third party.

543
00:34:24,544 --> 00:34:25,726
During the Lantern Festival

544
00:34:25,726 --> 00:34:27,747
she saw I put up lots of lanterns in my study.

545
00:34:27,747 --> 00:34:28,820
